    • createReturn

      private static String createReturn(Class<?> type)
      Constructs and returns method return-string. If type is boolean then returns CodeConstructor.TRUE; if type is byte, char, short, int, long, float or double then returns CodeConstructor.ZERO; else returns CodeConstructor.NULL.
      Parameters:
      type - type of method.
      Returns:
      method return-string starts with returns.
